 <p>
  Seemingly a rebranding of Nintendo Switch Online, which has been offering up select classic games since 2017, the Nintendo Classics app includes emulated versions of some of the best games of the Nintendo 64 era. A total of 34 Nintendo 64 games are currently available, including
