 </div>
 <p>
  <strong>
   Contraverse Hold - Warlock gauntlets
  </strong>
 </p>
 <p>
  <em>
   Exotic Perk
  </em>
  :
 </p>
 <ul>
  <li>
   <span class="display-card-hyperlink" data-id="703356" style="color: #ebc11d; ;">
